# project overview

this is a next.js e-commerce application for selling phones and accessories called "phono".

## key files

- [next.config.ts](mdc:next.config.ts): next.js configuration
- [package.json](mdc:package.json): project dependencies
- [tsconfig.json](mdc:tsconfig.json): typescript configuration
- [README.md](mdc:README.md): project documentation

## project structure

the project appears to use both the newer next.js app router (in `/app`) and the legacy pages router (in `/pages`).

shared components are located in the `/components` directory, while page-specific components are organized within their respective page directories.

see [structure.md](mdc:structure.md) for a complete directory structure.
